data.description: This stunning manufactured home has it all. The home boasts 3 beds, 2.5 baths and offers 2,221 sq ft of bright, polished living space. A spacious living area, impressive vaulted ceilings that enhance its spacious feel, and wood-look floors that blend seamlessly with any décor. The formal dining, open kitchen, and breakfast bar are the ideal setup for entertaining. The spacious laundry room leads to an enclosed covered patio  The large primary suite boasts a walk-in closet and a large bathtub. 2 car detached garage of nearly 900 sq ft with a finished office/workshop: front porch and covered back deck. Fully-fenced property on a 50,094 lot is ready for your family farm (RE1 zone) RV gate and mountain views. This is a must-see!
